    A reader weighs in on:
   </div>
   <div class="caption">
    <a href="https://blogs.berkeley.edu/2019/03/02/remembering-the-red-summer-of-1919/#div-comment-288593">
    </a>
    <div class="quotetitle">
     Remembering the Red Summer of 1919
    </div>
    <div class="quotename">
     Eleanore Lee said:
    </div>
    <blockquote>
     I think a new discussion of reparations is long overdue, as you say. My father's ancestors were slaveholders and Confederates. As a result I was raised, thinking about responsibility and what to do......
    </blockquote>
   </div>
  </div>
 </div>
</div>
